        "experiment_id": 1,
        "reaction_type": "低聚反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Oligomerization reaction",
        "description": "在ZSM-5沸石催化剂A上，研究轻质FCC汽油中烯烃的低聚反应。考察了温度（80-260°C）、压力（30-60 bar）和液时空速（1.0-2.0 h⁻¹）对烯烃转化率和产物选择性的影响。最佳条件为240°C，50 bar，液时空速2.0 h⁻¹，烯烃转化率为39.8%。",
        "text_snippet": "Investigating the temperature dependence of oligomerizing activity of zeolite A and B we found that the yield of the liquid products changed in range of 85-100%... The maximum value was achieved at 240°C and 50 bar.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Oligomer-Isomer reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "低聚反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Oligomerization reaction",
        "description": "在ZSM-5沸石催化剂B上，研究轻质FCC汽油中烯烃的低聚反应。考察了温度（180-300°C）、压力（30-60 bar）和液时空速（1.0-2.0 h⁻¹）对反应的影响。最佳条件为240°C，50 bar，液时空速2.0 h⁻¹，烯烃转化率为38.5%。",
        "text_snippet": "The results obtained on catalyst B are shown in Figures 6 and 7. The conversion of olefins was between 3% and 38.5%... Increase in pressure favoured for C12+ selectivity.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Oligomer-Isomer reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 3,
        "reaction_type": "低聚反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Oligomerization reaction",
        "description": "在由催化剂A和B组成的双层床催化剂系统上进行的低聚反应实验。最佳条件为270°C，40 bar，液时空速1.0 h⁻¹。在此条件下，烯烃转化率为33.5%，C12+选择性为18.2%，与单层床相比，中间馏分沸点范围内的低聚物比例大约翻倍。",
        "text_snippet": "During the two layered bed experiments, however, the C12+ selectivity was higher, at favourable conditions it approximately doubled in comparison to the value obtained with a single zeolite catalyst bed... The largest oligomer share in the product was reached at 270°C, 40 bar and 1.0 h-1 LHSV.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Oligomer-Isomer reaction"
      }
    ]
